{"tid":1055293,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"有冇手足對goose house有興趣到想過日本聽佢地可以幫幫我手？","createTime":"2019-03-10T12:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T21:38:40.000Z","uid":55960,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fbaaed4a39a193d270b94734bfb8a5ed828667d1","tid":1055293,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"雖然goose house已經解散左，但係作為一個fan都想支持單飛緊既成員<br />\n所以我決定遲啲去日本去聽佢唱歌<br />\n詳情:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.livepocket.jp/event/search?performer=%7B竹渕慶%7D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.livepocket.jp%2Fevent%2Fsearch%3Fperformer%3D%257B%E7%AB%B9%E6%B8%95%E6%85%B6%257D&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=5cd7bd92\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.livepocket.jp/event/search?performer=%7B竹渕慶%7D</a><br />\n<br />\n但係total有3場，我又戇居買晒3場<br />\n開頭以為可以抽中左先決定比唔比錢<br />\n但而家一次過買晒3場仲比埋錢<br />\n<br />\n所以想問下有冇手足係會喺4月5月既時候去名古屋/大阪/東京旅行，同時又會有興趣想去聽，唔想晒左舊錢又去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944fbcd20161d40d72729fb569eb11c5431a5349","tid":1055293,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63524c57c5fe5a6d7b95c8944f3f8ad99ddb48ef","tid":1055293,"uid":66076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T18:02:25.000Z","msg":"點解好哋哋要散？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110435d45f70c974757b4c9846f90e168124affe","tid":1055293,"uid":45217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T18:23:43.000Z","msg":"估唔到佢地會解散<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class